strings:
<voice_0x01000A6A><se_def>Lorenzo: Hold on there!
This is a family matter.
The lady will attend to you shortly.
<voice_0x01000A6B><se_high>Rosalind: I'm going to ask you again, Jessica.

<voice_0x01000A6C><se_high>Rosalind: Are you entirely bereft of compassion!?
Will you not mourn your own brother's death!?

<voice_0x01000A6D><se_high>Jessica: Not this, again!
Of course I'm sad!
I can't believe I even have to say it!

<voice_0x01000A6E><se_high>Jessica: But all you can think of is tradition and
family obligations! I'm talking about avenging
his murder!
<voice_0x01000A6F><se_high>Rosalind: Avenging...?

<voice_0x01000A70><se_high>Rosalind: You will stop this foolishness this instant!
You are a young lady, not a warrior!
<voice_0x01000A71><se_high>Rosalind: Do you really think Alistair would have wanted this? You will mourn your brother's death like a proper lady! It's our family's way.

<voice_0x01000A72><se_high>Jessica: Our family's way?
Who cares about our family's way!?

<voice_0x01000A73><se_high>Jessica: I don't expect you to believe me,
but Alistair spoke to me!
He told me to follow my heart.

<voice_0x01000A74><se_high>Jessica: That's why my mind is made up.
I don't care about the consequences.
I'm going to make Alistair's murderer pay.
<voice_0x01000A75>Rosalind: ......

<voice_0x01000A76><se_high>Rosalind: Very well.
It's obvious there's no talking to you.
Do as you wish.
<voice_0x01000A77><se_high>Rosalind: But...
<voice_0x01000A78><se_high>Rosalind: As far as I'm concerned, I no longer have a daughter! I want you out of this house at once!
<voice_0x01000A79><se_high>Jessica: Fine! I was planning on leaving until you came to your senses, anyway!

<voice_0x01000A7A><se_high>Jessica: Bangerz! Mash!
Let me through. I'm getting my things!
<voice_0x01000A7B><se_high>Jessica: I'm sorry for not telling you the truth before. Forgive me?
<voice_0x01000A7C><se_high>Bangerz: Are you really leavin', Jessica?

<voice_0x01000A7D><se_high>Jessica: Yes. I am. And I want you two to watch over
the village while I'm gone.

<voice_0x01000A7E><se_high>Jessica: Alistair told me this would happen.
He said you two would protect the town
and grow up to be famous warriors.
<voice_0x01000A7F><se_high>Mash: (Sob, sob...! Sniff...)
<voice_0x01000A80><se_high>Jessica: Come on. Chin up.

<voice_0x01000A81><se_high>Jessica: Your mission guarding my room is over.
I want you to patrol outside from now on!
<voice_0x01000A82><se_high>Bangerz: Yes, sir!
<voice_0x01000A83><se_high>Mash: (Sob!)

<voice_0x01000A84><se_high>Jessica: Well, I'm leaving!
Thanks for being such a great mum!
Have a nice life!
